title: Sawbones: Human Tricks
description: Can you touch your tongue with your nose or wiggle your ears? Dr. Sydnee and Justin talk about the science and studies behind weird little tricks some bodies can do, or "stupid human tricks." Can you flare your nostrils? author: Justin & Dr. Sydnee McElroy
